Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:43.94,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}絶望が塗り潰してく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.79,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.60,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:50.24,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}追いかけてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.96,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}夢も　理想も　情熱も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.49,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}またかき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.46,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}哀しい日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.05,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}いつかは終わりが來るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.17,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}迷いながら　もがきながら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:12.95,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}それでも　まだあきらめたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.89,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}傷だらけでも　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:19.89,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}この手のひらに 決して消えない星がある 　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.24,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}流れて墮ちた光は今も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:27.02,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}あの場所を遠く照らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:30.25,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}何度でも手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.49,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}今は描けなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:36.63,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}信じることが強さに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.94,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}輝いてよ　Shooting STAR
