Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.79,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.60,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:50.24,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}正在追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.96,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}梦想　理想　热情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.49,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}也全都消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.46,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悲伤的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:04.05,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}会不会有结束之日？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.17,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}迷惘着 挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:12.95,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使如此 也还不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.89,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:19.89,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在手中 仍有绝不会消失的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.24,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}滑落之后 那光芒现在也 　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:27.02,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}依然远远地照耀着那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:30.25,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}无数次伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:33.49,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使现在无法描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:36.63,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}信任会化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.94,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}闪耀吧 Shooting STAR
